This folder contains the drivers and the HAL interface. The drivers consist of low level
interfaces, such as UART, register read/write via memory mapping, I2C, etc. The framwork,
or API, to the boards is located in the property manager. The property maanager is the
API that is used to communicate with the state, properties of Crimson. If a configuration
parameter is not located in the property_manager.h interface, it cannot be configured.
